perties. This move aims to consolidate records like building maps, payment history, and legal status onto a single platform.  The initiative promises to significantly reduce paperwork, speed up verification, and combat fraud and ownership disputes, empowering buyers with clear legal status information before purchases.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/technology/lucknow-development-authority-introduces-unique-property-ids-to-combat-fraud-and-streamline-records/132091426?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-993631/132091426.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "technology"}]}